		"description": "<p>You have combined the power of your divine patron with a consistent regimen of martial training. &nbsp;You gain the following benefits:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Your Strength, Dexterity, or Wisdom score increases by 1, to a maximum of 20.</li>\n<li>You gain an additional Fighting Style based on your @UUID[Compendium.a5e.a5e-class-features.Item.orhewvz33vmmkfc5]{Defensive Blessing} choice.\n<ul>\n<li>If you chose @UUID[Compendium.a5e.a5e-class-features.Item.zyy0ne5b2afal0k9]{Armor of Conviction}, you gain your choice of @UUID[Compendium.a5e.a5e-class-features.Item.cyh3f0nnloa33u43]{Battle Ready} or @UUID[Compendium.a5e.a5e-class-features.Item.8go9z2qyufbmcens]{Unarmed Fighting}</li>\n<li>If you chose @UUID[Compendium.a5e.a5e-class-features.Item.yr4hno0hd2dco1ps]{Sacred Archery}, you gain your choice of @UUID[Compendium.a5e.a5e-class-features.Item.zwxerg4avwdez81a]{Archery} or @UUID[Compendium.a5e.a5e-class-features.Item.x6ekh3wi7ktnsh65]{Thrown Weapon Fighting}</li>\n<li>If you chose @UUID[Compendium.a5e.a5e-class-features.Item.cav9jrh671uz4ffu]{Spirit Soldier}, you gain your choice of @UUID[Compendium.a5e.a5e-class-features.Item.6ez2pap3b27morzt]{Defense} or @UUID[Compendium.a5e.a5e-class-features.Item.vhfr4oc5f411zi01]{Protection}</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>When you would gain a new Soldiering Knack or Sign of Faith, you can choose freely from either list.</li>\n</ul>",
